import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Form,
  InputContainer,
  UserImg,
  UserInfo,
  UserText,
  UserTextBox,
  Wrap,
} from "./styled";
import {
  Button,
  ContentContainer,
  Hr,
  Input,
  Label,
  Title,
} from "src/commonStyles";
import { SubmitHandler, useForm } from "react-hook-form";

interface IFormInput {
  firstName: string;
  lastName: string;
  birthday: string;
  sex: string;
  country: string;
  login: string;
  email: string;
}

export default function PersonalCabinet() {
  const {
    register,
    handleSubmit,
    formState: { errors },
    reset,
  } = useForm<IFormInput>();

  const onSubmit: SubmitHandler<IFormInput> = (data) => {
    console.log(data);
    reset();
  };

  return (
    <Wrap>
      <ContentContainer>
        <Title>Личный кабинет</Title>
        <Hr />
        <UserInfo>
          <UserImg $backgroundImg="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1633332755192-727a05c4013d?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mnx8dXNlcnxlbnwwfHwwfHx8MA%3D%3D&w=1000&q=80" />
          <UserTextBox>
            <UserText>Иванов Иван</UserText>
            <UserText>id:123</UserText>
          </UserTextBox>
        </UserInfo>
        <Form>
          <Container>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Имя
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Фамилия
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
          </Container>
          <Container>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Дата рождения
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Пол
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
          </Container>
          <Container>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Страна
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Город
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="349px" />
            </InputContainer>
          </Container>
          <Container>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                Логин
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="753px" />
            </InputContainer>
          </Container>
          <Container>
            <InputContainer>
              <Label htmlFor="" $height="43px">
                E-mail
              </Label>
              <Input id="" $width="753px" />
            </InputContainer>
          </Container>
          <Button type="submit">Сохранить</Button>
        </Form>
      </ContentContainer>
    </Wrap>
  );
}
